\v 24 Je² Ni³na¹ xi³ cjai¹nca³ tjin¹-le⁴ nca³nˀion¹, nca³ va³se²chjoa²-no³ nca³ tsi² tsa² tsao⁴nquio³, nca³ si⁴²qui³ncha¹-no³ nqui³xcon⁴ cjoa⁴je³ya³-le⁴ cao⁴ cjai¹nca³ tse³ cjoa⁴tsjoa³ nca³ tsi²jme³ je¹ xi³ tjin¹-no³.
\v 25 Je² Ni³na¹ xi³ ña³qui³ nca³ to⁴je² xi³ chji⁴ne⁴, xi³ vˀa³sje³ntjai²-na¹, ca²ta³vi³tjo³ncˀa³, ca²ta³ma³je³ya³, ca²ta³va³te¹xo³ma³, ca²ta³sˀe³-le⁴ nca³nˀion¹ ntˀai⁴-vi⁴ cao⁴ nca³ntsjai². Cˀoa⁴ ca²ta³ma³.
